A Rubyesque interface to Google's GMail, with all the tools you'll
need. Search, read and send multipart emails, archive, mark as
read/unread, delete emails, and manage labels.

It's based on Daniel Parker's ruby-gmail gem. This version has more
friendy API, is well tested, better documented and have many other
improvements.

WWW: https://github.com/nu7hatch/gmail
